      "content": "i mean i get what you're saying but i really dont want to deal with doctors right now. is there like a specific type of eye drop i can get at the pharmacy that actually kills bacteria? if i just get some antibiotic drops from the drugstore myself, wouldn't that be just as good as a prescription? i just want to fix this quickly so i can get back to work.",
